verbs.description: [ARG0: russian and egyptian presidents] [V: sign] [ARG1: partnership treaty] russian president vladimir putin and egyptian president abdel - fattah el - sissi signed a strategic cooperation treaty wednesday that is intended to bolster trade and other ties between the two nations the treaty capped a three - day visit to russia by the egyptian leader during his talks with putin on wednesday el - sissi also urged russia to resume direct flights to egyptian resorts which moscow suspended after a bomb planted by the islamic state group brought a russian plane down over sinai in october 2015 killing all 224 people on board abdel - fattah el - sissi egypt cairo moscow vladimir putin russia
